      "title": "Council Chief Minister, Chief Whip appointed",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Finance Minister Sushil Premajayantha has been appointed as the chief minister and Prasanna Ranatunga as the chief whip of the ruling party."
      ],
